cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image fusion using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a segmentation approach and a weighted average rule also suggests the paper could be categorized under machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The end-to-end training of the network and the use of a regression-based fusion function suggest the paper could also be categorized under deep learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
